=3DWhat+I%27m+Hearing+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%287%2F19%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_ac=
tion&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a )that =E2=80=9C=
Zaslav was examining several strategic options, ranging from selling assets=
 to hiving off its Warner Bros. movie studio and Max streaming service into=
 a new company unburdened by most of the group=E2=80=99s current $39 billio=
n net debt load.=E2=80=9D

If that potential plan sounds familiar, it=E2=80=99s because some analysts =
and hedge fund managers suggested Disney should do something similar last y=
ear: essentially, put the declining TV assets and the debt on the corporate=
