g growth assets, thus creating a =E2=80=9Cclean=E2=80=9D company with a str=
ong narrative. Bob
Iger ultimately decided not to do that or sell the TV networks outright.

But Zaslav, perhaps admitting that the grand plan to mash up Discovery=E2=
=80=99s lowbrow reality shows with the prestige of HBO and the Warner Bros.=
